msgstr "Ladrillos de pizarra profunda"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_deepslate/deepslate.lua:118
msgid "Deepslate bricks are the brick version of deepslate."
msgstr "Los ladrillos deepslate son la versión en ladrillo de la deepslate."

